The Facebook post by Regia Nationala a Padurilor - Romsilva is a paid advertisement showcasing the beauty of Romanian forests.  It does not mention any political candidates or parties, nor does it attempt to influence voters in any election. The content is primarily informational and promotional, focusing on Romsilva's role in managing Romania's forests.  While the post falls under the "POLITICAL" category due to the nature of Facebook's ad categorization, its content itself does not constitute electoral propaganda as defined by Article 98 t) of LEGE nr. 208 din 20 iulie 2015.
